sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Pytest as Pytest runner
    participant ProcFactory as dynamodb_proc fixture
    participant DDBProcess as DynamoDB Local process
    participant ResourceFactory as dynamodb resource fixture
    participant DynamoDB as DynamoDB tables

    Pytest->>ProcFactory: request dynamodb_proc
    ProcFactory->>DDBProcess: start process
    loop per test
        Pytest->>ResourceFactory: request dynamodb resource
        ResourceFactory->>DDBProcess: connect with boto3 resource
        Pytest->>DynamoDB: run test using tables
        Pytest->>DynamoDB: teardown: delete all tables
    end
